text: @UPSHelp I have a few packages  arriving today. I live in a secured apartment building. I hope I get my stuff today, as no real way to say when the truck will be around.
@punkeymonkey529 How does the driver access the building? Is there some sort of code or something required?^DS

@UPSHelp there's no code. sometimes i think the main door is open to intercom,  sometimes it's locked like it should be. I very early order stuff so not sure how they handle deliveries. most of the time I see others leave notes on the main door
@UPSHelp can I get a smaller time frame on my delivery? I'll be getting off the night shift, and need to gets little sleep, but would like my stuff today as it's hard for me to get to ups pu office.

@punkeymonkey529 Due to day-to-day variations in package volume, driver delivery routes, driver pickup routes, and your location on these routes; UPS is unable to provide or schedule a specific delivery time.^DS
@punkeymonkey529 Deliveries are made from 9:00AM to 8:00PM, & sometimes later depending on the driver's truckload.^DS
